====Usage notes====
This is one of a few everyday kanji with a five-[[mora]] reading, and one of only three nouns. The only other kanji with five-mora readings are {{lang|ja|承}} in the verb {{ja-r|承る|うけたまわる}}, {{lang|ja|慮}} in the verb {{ja-r|慮る|おもんぱかる}}, {{ja-r|志|こころざし}}, {{ja-r|政|まつりごと}}, and {{ja-r|詔|みことのり}} (also written as {{ja-r|勅|みことのり}}). No kanji in common use has a six- or more mora reading.

